                                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                                <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Find a clean and quiet venue</li>
                                                <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Use a simple, light-colored background</li>
                                                <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Position the light source in front of you</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
