                                                <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Make a test call to check your equipment one day before</li>
                                                <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Adjust your webcam to frame your face</li>
                                                <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Check your privacy settings to make sure you can receive the interviewer’s call</li>
