                                        <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Dress the part</li>
                                        <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Speak clearly and with a positive tone</li>
                                        <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Look at the camera, not the screen</li>
                                        <li><i class="ti-check-box"></i> Nod your head to show understanding</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>



                        </div>
                    </div>


                    <div class="row my-1">
                        <div class="col-sm-8 text-center bg-success  center-block py-1">

